org.decomposer.math.vector
Interface MapVector

All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<IntDoublePair>
All Known Implementing Classes:
DenseMapVector, HashMapVector, ImmutableSparseMapVector
public interface MapVector
extends java.lang.Iterable<IntDoublePair>, java.lang.Cloneable

Basic interface for mathematical vectors (elements of a finite dimensional linear vector space). Effectively extends Map, but is not really a true member of the java.util.collections api. Different implementations may be tuned toward sparsity, immutability, or maximum flexibility.
